title: High-efficiency LED lighting, Lounge with a chef's kitchen
posting_body: ['The Eddy', '10 New Street , East Boston, MA, 02128', 'Use the link below for more details:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', '(617) 380-4884 x 6', 'OR Text', '6', 'to', '(617) 380-4884', 'to contact us.', 'Welcome home to The Eddy', 'This is a Studio, 1 Bath, approximately 388.0 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'The Eddy is located along the waterfront in East Boston, boasting unrivaled views of the Boston skyline and within walking distance to an eclectic mix of restaurants, shops and entertainment.', "The Eddy is transit-oriented and serves as a bridge between Boston's most vibrant neighborhoods.", 'Pricing and availability subject to change.', 'Features', '- Locally-sourced and recycled-content materials', '- Energy Star-rated appliances', '- High-efficiency LED lighting', '- Well-designed living spaces', '- Low-flow fixtures', '- Nest Learning Thermostats™', 'Community Amenities', '- Dog wash', '- Well-served by transit through the blue line, an expanded water taxi station, highways and Logan Airport', '- Bike maintenance facilities', '- Fireplace', '- Secure bike parking', '- Rooftop deck with seating and 270° views', '- Access to a new waterfront park', '- Pet-friendly', '- Grilling stations', '- Private conference rooms', '- Modern fitness facilities', '- Sun deck', '- Poolside restaurant service for residents', '- Direct access to Lo Presti Park', '- Waterfront property with uninterrupted views of the Boston Harbor and city skyline', '- Outdoor terrace', '- Pool', '- Music room', '- On-site restaurant with indoor and outdoor dining spaces', '- Car sharing options', '- Access to boat landing', "- Lounge with a chef's kitchen", 'UTxaE6gAN']
